title: Plasmafox-ReCore.[Portable-Browser-Games-tv-streaming]
description:
Plasmafox isn't just a regular Internet browser, it's a lite fast portable browser that allows you to stream games and cable channels without any installations




##Features## 

Super fast and lite Internet Browser than can also run from your USB.
 
Stream and play Over 20 playable games and indie games such as AVGN, Metal Slug 4, Star Wars Arcade, DBZ, Limbo and more ( Server will soon be updated).

Stream free cable channels like Nickelodeon, USA network, Wrestling and more.

No installations required.

for PC, Linux and Mac
